(511738, 'Chocolate Java Protein Shake', 'Chocolate Java Protein Shake might be just the <b>Southern</b> recipe you are searching for. This gluten free recipe serves 1 and costs <b>$1.43 per serving</b>. One portion of this dish contains roughly <b>27g of protein</b>, <b>5g of fat</b>, and a total of <b>257 calories</b>. 1 person has tried and liked this recipe. If you have chocolate chips, ice, coffee, and a few other ingredients on hand, you can make it. Not a lot of people really liked this beverage. It is brought to you by Pick Fresh Foods. From preparation to the plate, this recipe takes roughly <b>45 minutes</b>. With a spoonacular <b>score of 78%</b>, this dish is good. Similar recipes include <a href=\"https://spoonacular.com/recipes/chocolate-java-protein-shake-1744221\">Chocolate Java Protein Shake</a>, <a href=\"https://spoonacular.com/recipes/almond-joy-breakfast-shake-chocolate-coconut-protein-shake-996923\">Almond Joy Breakfast Shake â€“ Chocolate Coconut Protein Shake</a>, and <a href=\"https://spoonacular.com/recipes/the-best-chocolate-protein-shake-1161368\">The Best Chocolate Protein Shake</a>.', '\"Add ingredients in the order listed into a blender.Blend until smooth.Enjoy!\"', 'https://img.spoonacular.com/recipes/511738-556x370.jpg', '[{\"id\":10019146,\"aisle\":\"Baking\",\"image\":\"chocolate-chips.jpg\",\"consistency\":\"SOLID\",\"name\":\"chocolate chips\",\"nameClean\":\"mini chocolate chips\",\"original\":\"1 Tbsp mini chocolate chips\",\"originalName\":\"mini chocolate chips\",\"amount\":1,\"unit\":\"Tbsp\",\"meta\":[\"mini\"],\"measures\":{\"us\":{\"amount\":1,\"unitShort\":\"Tbsp\",\"unitLong\":\"Tbsp\"},\"metric\":{\"amount\":1,\"unitShort\":\"Tbsp\",\"unitLong\":\"Tbsp\"}}},{\"id\":99075,\"aisle\":\"Health Foods\",\"image\":\"chocolate-protein-powder.jpg\",\"consistency\":\"SOLID\",\"name\":\"chocolate protein powder\",\"nameClean\":\"chocolate protein powder\",\"original\":\"1 scoop Chocolate protein powder\",\"originalName\":\"Chocol